memberdef.name: DataIterator

detaileddescription.para: (startingFileOffset, startingRecordOffset) points to the next row that reader should resume from. E.g., if the seek position is (file=0, record=1), seek moves the iterator position to the 2nd row in file 0. When next() is called after seek, 2nd row from file 0 should be returned.
